Kenneth Utt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kenneth_Utt 0 Kenneth Utt (July 13, 1921 – January 19, 1994), was an American film producer and unit production manager, notable for producing The Silence of the Lambs (1991), for which he won an Oscar for Best Picture.
